Cannot we yet ſee, what Obſtructions and Blocks are laid in our Way? Who are the Actors and Managers of the Scene? They appear in as full, and Open view to us, as the Stars in a clear Froſty Night, notwithſtanding the Various and Changeable Maſks they Cover their Faces with, and pretty faſhionable, plauſible Attire they appear of Late in: Therefore our Way is ſhort and plain; and if we Now ſet out in the right path; I hope before May next be wholly Expired, we ſhall have got almoſt to our Journey's End, and ſhall then Once more have this Province diſengaged from its preſent Incumberances, and the Induſtrious well minded Man freed from the Jaws of the Oppreſſ
                     •
                  r. I ſhall add no more at preſent, but Subſcribe my ſelf as really I am;
